  "policyPrivacyTitle": "Privacy Policy",
  "policyPrivacyEffectiveDate": "January 30, 2026",
  "policyPrivacySectionIntroTitle": "Introduction",
  "policyPrivacySectionIntroContent": "FlirtFix (\"we\", \"our\", or \"us\") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application FlirtFix (the \"App\"). Please read this policy carefully. If you do not agree with these terms, please do not access the App.",
  "policyPrivacySectionInfoCollectTitle": "1. Information We Collect",
  "policyPrivacySectionInfoCollectContent": "We collect information you provide directly to us when using FlirtFix:\n\n- Account information: email address, username, and password (hashed and securely stored)\n- Conversation data: messages and conversation text submitted for AI analysis\n- Uploaded content: screenshots and profile images you upload for analysis\n- Device information: Android device ID for device identification\n- Usage data: information about how you interact with the app\n- Payment information: purchase tokens, transaction IDs, and subscription status through Google Play Billing",
  "policyPrivacySectionInfoUseTitle": "2. How We Use Your Information",
  "policyPrivacySectionInfoUseContent": "We use collected information to:\n\n- Provide AI-powered conversation assistance and suggestions\n- Analyze uploaded images and screenshots\n- Manage your account and subscription\n- Process payments and billing\n- Improve and optimize our app and services\n- Communicate updates, features, and support\n- Enforce fair use and terms\n- Comply with legal obligations",
  "policyPrivacySectionThirdPartyTitle": "3. Third-Party Services",
  "policyPrivacySectionThirdPartyContent": "We use third-party services that may collect information about you:\n\n- Firebase Analytics for app usage analytics\n- Firebase Crashlytics for crash reporting and stability\n- Google Play Billing for subscriptions and in-app purchases\n\nThese services have their own privacy policies.",
  "policyPrivacySectionStorageSecurityTitle": "4. Data Storage and Security",
  "policyPrivacySectionStorageSecurityContent": "Your data is stored both locally on your device and on secure servers:\n\n- Local storage: auth tokens, profile data, credits, and preferences\n- Server storage: account information, conversation history, and uploaded images\n- Security measures: token-based auth, HTTPS encryption, and standard technical safeguards",
  "policyPrivacySectionRetentionTitle": "5. Data Retention",
  "policyPrivacySectionRetentionContent": "We retain personal information while your account is active or as needed to provide services. When you delete your account:\n\n- Personal information is removed from our servers\n- Uploaded images and conversation history are deleted\n- Local data is cleared from your device\n- Some backup data may be retained for up to 30 days",
  "policyPrivacySectionRightsTitle": "6. Your Rights",
  "policyPrivacySectionRightsContent": "You may request access, correction, deletion, portability, or objection regarding your personal information. Contact us at support@tryagaintext.com to exercise these rights.",
  "policyPrivacySectionComplianceTitle": "7. GDPR and CCPA Compliance",
  "policyPrivacySectionComplianceContent": "For users in the EU and California, we process personal data lawfully, fairly, and transparently. We do not sell personal information and honor applicable legal rights.",
  "policyPrivacySectionCookiesTitle": "8. Cookies and Tracking",
  "policyPrivacySectionCookiesContent": "The app uses Firebase Analytics and similar technologies to track usage patterns, analyze feature performance, and identify technical issues.",
  "policyPrivacySectionChildrenTitle": "9. Children's Privacy",
  "policyPrivacySectionChildrenContent": "FlirtFix is intended for users age 18 and older. We do not knowingly collect personal information from anyone under 18.",
  "policyPrivacySectionSharingTitle": "10. Data Sharing and Disclosure",
  "policyPrivacySectionSharingContent": "We do not sell or rent personal information. We may share data only with service providers, when required by law, to protect rights/safety, or during business transfers.",
  "policyPrivacySectionTransfersTitle": "11. International Data Transfers",
  "policyPrivacySectionTransfersContent": "Your information may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your country of residence, where data protection laws may differ.",
  "policyPrivacySectionChangesTitle": "12. Changes to This Privacy Policy",
  "policyPrivacySectionChangesContent": "We may update this policy from time to time. We will update the effective date and post changes in the app. Continued use after changes become effective means acceptance.",
  "policyPrivacySectionContactTitle": "13. Contact Us",
  "policyPrivacySectionContactContent": "If you have questions, contact support@tryagaintext.com. Company: FlirtFix.",

  "policyTermsTitle": "Terms of Use",
  "policyTermsEffectiveDate": "January 30, 2026",
  "policyTermsSectionAgreementTitle": "Agreement to Terms",
  "policyTermsSectionAgreementContent": "By accessing and using FlirtFix, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Use. If you do not agree, do not use the app.",
  "policyTermsSectionServiceDescriptionTitle": "1. Service Description",
  "policyTermsSectionServiceDescriptionContent": "FlirtFix is an AI-powered mobile app that provides conversation assistance, screenshot OCR, profile analysis, custom instruction support, and subscription-based access subject to fair use limits.",
  "policyTermsSectionAcceptableUseTitle": "2. Acceptable Use Policy",
  "policyTermsSectionAcceptableUseContent": "You may not use FlirtFix for harassment, illegal activity, policy circumvention, reverse engineering, bot access, or commercial resale of generated content.",
  "policyTermsSectionFairUseTitle": "3. Fair Use Policy",
  "policyTermsSectionFairUseContent": "Unlimited plans are subject to fair use limits, including daily and weekly usage controls and abuse detection. Excessive abuse may lead to temporary restriction or termination.",
  "policyTermsSectionRegistrationTitle": "4. Account Registration",
  "policyTermsSectionRegistrationContent": "You must be at least 18, provide accurate information, protect your credentials, and remain responsible for account activity.",
  "policyTermsSectionSubscriptionTitle": "5. Subscription Terms",
  "policyTermsSectionSubscriptionContent": "FlirtFix Unlimited is billed weekly through Google Play Billing with auto-renewal unless canceled. Pricing and availability may change with notice.",
  "policyTermsSectionIpRightsTitle": "6. Intellectual Property Rights",
  "policyTermsSectionIpRightsContent": "You retain ownership of your uploaded content. FlirtFix retains ownership of the app, branding, algorithms, and related intellectual property.",
  "policyTermsSectionDisclaimerTitle": "7. Disclaimer of Warranties",
  "policyTermsSectionDisclaimerContent": "The app is provided \"as is\" and \"as available\" without warranties. AI suggestions are guidance only and do not guarantee outcomes.",
  "policyTermsSectionLiabilityTitle": "8. Limitation of Liability",
  "policyTermsSectionLiabilityContent": "To the maximum extent permitted by law, FlirtFix is not liable for indirect or consequential damages. Liability is limited to amounts paid in the prior 12 months.",
  "policyTermsSectionAvailabilityTitle": "9. Service Availability",
  "policyTermsSectionAvailabilityContent": "Service may be interrupted for maintenance, updates, or third-party limitations. We do not guarantee uninterrupted availability.",
  "policyTermsSectionTerminationTitle": "10. Termination",
  "policyTermsSectionTerminationContent": "We may suspend or terminate access for policy violations, fraud, legal requirements, or product discontinuation.",
  "policyTermsSectionLawTitle": "11. Governing Law and Jurisdiction",
  "policyTermsSectionLawContent": "These terms are governed by the laws of the United States.",
  "policyTermsSectionDisputeTitle": "12. Dispute Resolution",
  "policyTermsSectionDisputeContent": "Before legal action, contact support@tryagaintext.com for informal resolution. Unresolved disputes may proceed as allowed by applicable law and platform policy.",
  "policyTermsSectionChangesTitle": "13. Changes to Terms",
  "policyTermsSectionChangesContent": "We may modify these terms at any time and update the effective date in-app. Continued use indicates acceptance.",
  "policyTermsSectionSeverabilityTitle": "14. Severability",
  "policyTermsSectionSeverabilityContent": "If one provision is unenforceable, the remaining provisions remain in effect.",
  "policyTermsSectionEntireAgreementTitle": "15. Entire Agreement",
  "policyTermsSectionEntireAgreementContent": "These Terms, together with our Privacy and Refund policies, form the entire agreement between you and FlirtFix.",
  "policyTermsSectionContactTitle": "16. Contact Information",
  "policyTermsSectionContactContent": "For questions about these Terms, contact support@tryagaintext.com.",

  "policyRefundTitle": "Refund Policy",
  "policyRefundEffectiveDate": "January 30, 2026",
  "policyRefundSectionOverviewTitle": "Overview",
  "policyRefundSectionOverviewContent": "This Refund Policy explains subscription and purchase refund handling. Transactions are processed via Google Play Billing and may also be subject to Google Play rules.",
  "policyRefundSectionSubscriptionRefundsTitle": "1. Subscription Refunds",
  "policyRefundSectionSubscriptionRefundsContent": "Initial subscription refunds may be requested within the platform's allowed window and are subject to eligibility and usage review.",
  "policyRefundSectionGooglePlayProcessTitle": "2. Google Play Refund Process",
  "policyRefundSectionGooglePlayProcessContent": "To request a refund, use Google Play subscription management or account help pages and follow the refund workflow provided by Google Play.",
  "policyRefundSectionCreditRefundsTitle": "3. Credit Purchase Refunds",
  "policyRefundSectionCreditRefundsContent": "Credit purchases are generally non-refundable once delivered, except where required by law or in confirmed technical delivery failures.",
  "policyRefundSectionEligibilityTitle": "4. Refund Eligibility",
  "policyRefundSectionEligibilityContent": "Refund eligibility depends on purchase timing, usage, and policy compliance. Fraud, abuse, or policy violations may void eligibility.",
  "policyRefundSectionCancellationTitle": "5. Subscription Cancellation",
  "policyRefundSectionCancellationContent": "You may cancel any time through Google Play. Cancellation stops future renewals and access typically remains until period end.",
  "policyRefundSectionBillingIssuesTitle": "6. Billing Issues",
  "policyRefundSectionBillingIssuesContent": "For duplicate or unexpected charges, contact support@tryagaintext.com with transaction details and also review Google Play account purchase history.",
  "policyRefundSectionProcessingTimeTitle": "7. Refund Processing Time",
  "policyRefundSectionProcessingTimeContent": "Refund processing times vary by provider and financial institution and may take several business days.",
  "policyRefundSectionExceptionsTitle": "8. Exceptions and Special Cases",
  "policyRefundSectionExceptionsContent": "Extended outages, incorrect billing, and verified technical failures may be reviewed for prorated or full refund exceptions.",
  "policyRefundSectionFairUseAbuseTitle": "9. Fair Use and Abuse",
  "policyRefundSectionFairUseAbuseContent": "Repeated refund abuse, policy violations, or fraudulent use may result in denial of refund requests and account restriction.",
  "policyRefundSectionThirdPartyIssuesTitle": "10. Third-Party Payment Issues",
  "policyRefundSectionThirdPartyIssuesContent": "Google Play has final authority on payment and charge disputes for transactions processed through its billing platform.",
  "policyRefundSectionNoRefundScenariosTitle": "11. No Refund Scenarios",
  "policyRefundSectionNoRefundScenariosContent": "Refunds are generally not available for change of mind after substantial use, subjective dissatisfaction, or missed cancellation before renewal.",
  "policyRefundSectionDisputeTitle": "12. Dispute Resolution",
  "policyRefundSectionDisputeContent": "If a refund request is denied, contact support with additional details. If unresolved, dispute options may be available through the payment platform.",
  "policyRefundSectionPolicyChangesTitle": "13. Policy Changes",
  "policyRefundSectionPolicyChangesContent": "We may update this policy and publish changes in-app with an updated effective date.",
  "policyRefundSectionContactTitle": "14. Contact for Refund Requests",
  "policyRefundSectionContactContent": "For refund requests or questions, email support@tryagaintext.com with your transaction details.",

